{"tid":2050940,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返新工對住班老屎忽真係好頹","createTime":"2020-06-04T12:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T17:41:52.000Z","uid":36496,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"351146a48fb9c25a5314d0e78ca8f74629102cac","tid":2050940,"uid":36496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"之前份工係大公司, 大部份同事都係二十幾三十歲既後生仔女, 大家都好岩傾, 做野做到攰可以吹下水講下笑. 放工有時都約埋一班人食飯.<br />\n星期一轉工, 去左間細公司, 得十幾人. 全部同事都係四十幾五十歲. 其實佢地無咩野, 但真係有代溝, 無咩話題. 每日就係不停工作工作, 返工放工. <br />\n<br />\n我明白而家我返工係為左賺錢, 唔係識朋友. 工作性質一樣, 但個落差真係好大, 日日返工都好頹好無動力, 有種等退休既感覺. 返左幾年工, 第一次意識到原來同事, 工作環境係咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc05a116a70f7c7b48ea7a0c30450aca30f0b2ba","tid":2050940,"uid":90403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffea4f0cd87c74b0e5754501366b05c4bcc1b43b","tid":2050940,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"點解轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d554328750f0ff8084cd38a1c61b283b94cff70","tid":2050940,"uid":36496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc05a116a70f7c7b48ea7a0c30450aca30f0b2ba","tid":2050940,"uid":90403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"Title叫升左職, 加左少少人工."},{"pid":"69890459a1e2167f3facda489e7902fe72f55a3d","tid":2050940,"uid":36496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffea4f0cd87c74b0e5754501366b05c4bcc1b43b","tid":2050940,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"點解轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}